Author-Name: GUISAN, Maria-Carmen
Author-Email: 
Keywords:  
Title: Presentation: International Perspectives
Abstract: For the first time, in 23 years of life of journal RGE, we have the opportunity to launch an special issue on international perspectives in English. Until now the journal has published many interesting articles with regional, national and international perspective in Spanish. This is an step to a higher level of internationalization of the Revista Galega de Economia/Economic Review of Galicia, both to foster the international readership of interesting publications by researchers from this region and country and the publication of international perspectives for development from other countries. In this presentation we present a summary of the main contributions of this issue and some references to the history of our journal.
