Author-Name: Calvo Babío, Nuria
Author-Email:
Author-Name: Dávila Aparicio, Raúl
Author-Email:
Keywords: Business strategy, Organizational design, Business cooperation, Innovation.
Title: COOPERATION OF GALICIAN COMPANIES AS COMPETITIVE SURVIVAL. THE CASE OF CENOR
Abstract: The current economic difficulties are helping what years ago professionals considered impossible: galician SME are collaborating in a competitive environment. In this work, the authors have analysed the strategic integration process of the company Hermanos Pena S.L. in the group CENOR. The authors have developed a previous diagnosis of the sectorial cooperation and the organizational tendency to collaborate of the company. They have also proposed a new methodology aimed to promote cooperation and professionalization of SMEs.
