Keywords: Competitiveness / Strategy of Lisbon / Galicia / Country image / Productivity
Title: COMPETITIVENESS OF GALICIAN FIRMS IN THE CONTEXT OF THE STRATEGY OF LISBON
Abstract: The international crisis is slowing down the strategic decision making about the economic and social future. This work is a discussion about their potential effects in Galician firms competitiveness.
