Author-Email: 
Author-Name: Rey Suárez, Pedro María
Author-Email: 
Keywords: Labor market / Activity / Employment / Unemployment / Training / Qualification / Labor costs / Wages / Productivity
Title: THE GALICIAN LABOR MARKET SINCE THE ENTRY INTO EUROPE
Abstract: This article reflects on Galician labor market since the mid-eighties, comparing it with the Spanish labor market, based on the results of available official statistics. We analise the evolution of the key variables that define this market and discuss the specificities presented in Galicia.
